Package no.ntnu.idatx1005.observer

Class ButtonClickHandler

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatx1005.observer.ButtonClickHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ButtonClickObserver
public class ButtonClickHandler extends Object implements ButtonClickObserver

ButtonClickHandler class

This class is responsible for handling button click events and managing navigation through the ViewNavigator. It also handles the logic for updating the view based on the button clicked. This class implements the ButtonClickObserver interface.

Since:
V1.1.0
Author:
Tord Fosse
